2026-05-07T23:19:02.9570593Z 13    <!--
2026-05-07T23:19:02.9571231Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-07T23:19:02.9572293Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
