2026-05-07T23:19:02.9581134Z 22    <!--
2026-05-07T23:19:02.9581774Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-07T23:19:02.9582949Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-07T23:19:02.9583702Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-07T23:19:02.9584614Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-07T23:19:02.9585651Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-07T23:19:02.9586555Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-07T23:19:02.9587455Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-07T23:19:02.9588429Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-07T23:19:02.9589328Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-07T23:19:02.9590180Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-07T23:19:02.9590851Z 33    -->
